---
import ContentLayout from "../layouts/ContentLayout.astro";
---

<ContentLayout
    title="Events"
    description="Join the Green Schools Foundation at our community events supporting student success in Green Local Schools."
    showBreadcrumbs={true}
    breadcrumbs={[
        { name: "Events", href: "/events" }
    ]}
>
    <div class="content-section">
        <h2>GSF Community Events</h2>
        <p>
            The Green Schools Foundation hosts events throughout the year to bring our community together, celebrate student achievements, and raise funds to support scholarships, classroom grants, and educational programs in Green Local Schools.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid-2">
        <!-- Battle of the Slice -->
        <a href="/battle-of-the-slice" class="block bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300 group">
            <div class="aspect-video bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center p-6">
                <img
                    src="/images/Battle of the Slice.jpg"
                    alt="Green's Battle of the Slice"
                    class="max-h-full max-w-full object-contain group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300"
                />
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2 group-hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">Battle of the Slice</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">
                    Taste your way through the area's best pizzas, enjoy games and activities for all ages, and support student success—one delicious slice at a time!
                </p>
                <span class="text-primary-600 font-semibold text-sm group-hover:text-primary-700">
                    Learn More →
                </span>
            </div>
        </a>

        <!-- Celebration of Education -->
        <a href="/celebration-of-education" class="block bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300 group">
            <div class="aspect-video bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-accent-500 flex items-center justify-center p-6">
                <div class="text-center text-white">
                    <svg class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"/>
                    </svg>
                    <span class="text-lg font-semibold">Annual Gala</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2 group-hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">Celebration of Education</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">
                    Our signature annual event recognizing outstanding students, educators, and community supporters while presenting scholarships to graduating seniors.
                </p>
                <span class="text-primary-600 font-semibold text-sm group-hover:text-primary-700">
                    Learn More →
                </span>
            </div>
        </a>
    </div>

    <div class="highlight-box mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-4">Support Our Events</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
            All proceeds from GSF events go directly to supporting scholarships, academic classroom grants, and educational programs for students in the Green Local School District.
        </p>
        <div class="grid-2">
            <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Become a Sponsor</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-4">
                    Partner with us and gain visibility in the community while supporting student success.
                </p>
                <a href="mailto:greenschoolsfoundation@gmail.com?subject=Event Sponsorship Inquiry" class="button-primary">
                    Sponsorship Info
                </a>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Volunteer</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-4">
                    Help make our events successful by volunteering your time and talents.
                </p>
                <a href="mailto:greenschoolsfoundation@gmail.com?subject=Event Volunteer Inquiry" class="button-secondary">
                    Get Involved
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section text-center">
        <h2>Stay Updated on Events</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
            Don't miss out on upcoming GSF events! Follow our blog for the latest news and announcements.
        </p>
        <a href="/blog" class="button-primary">Read Our Blog</a>
    </div>
</ContentLayout>
